    SELECT r0."RoleId", r0."EndpointGroupId", r0."IsActive", e."Id", e."CreatedBy", e."DateCreated", e."DateDeleted", e."DateUpdated", e."Description", e."IsActive" AS "IsActive0", e."IsDeleted", e."Name", t1."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t1."EndpointId", t1."IsActive" AS "IsActive1", t1."Id" AS "Id0", t1."CreatedBy" AS "CreatedBy0", t1."DateCreated" AS "DateCreated0", t1."DateDeleted" AS "DateDeleted0", t1."DateUpdated" AS "DateUpdated0", t1."Description" AS "Description0", t1."IsActive0" AS "IsActive00", t1."IsDeleted" AS "IsDeleted0", t1."Name" AS "Name0", t1."Path", t1."Type"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e0."EndpointGroupId", e0."EndpointId", e0."IsActive", e1."Id", e1."CreatedBy", e1."DateCreated", e1."DateDeleted", e1."DateUpdated", e1."Description", e1."IsActive" AS "IsActive0", e1."IsDeleted", e1."Name", e1."Path", e1."Type"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
    ) AS t1 ON e."Id" = t1."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."RoleId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."EndpointId"

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (

    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"

        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"

) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"

) AS t

    SELECT p0."Id", p0."AddedByUserId", p0."DeletedByUserId", p0."IsDeleted", p0."PlayerId", p0."SegmentId", s."Id" AS "Id0", s."CreatedByUserId", s."Description", s."PriorityLevel"
    FROM "PlayerSegments" AS p0
    LEFT JOIN "Segments" AS s ON p0."SegmentId" = s."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."PlayerId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."Id"

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (

    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0

FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))

FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"
